          "title": "Get Your API Key",
          "summary": "Obtain an API key from the dashboard",
          "content": "To use the ACME API, you need an API key.\n\n1. Log in to your [ACME Dashboard](https://dashboard.acme.example)\n2. Navigate to Settings > API Keys\n3. Click \"Create New Key\"\n4. Copy the key - you won't see it again!"
        },
        {
          "id": "first-request",
